{
  "stem": "9113.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was maybe September-- September the 1st when the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe September the 4th we came to that little town, and over there was a big fight between the Polish army and the German army.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Didn't last too long.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Overnight was over, but we-- we had a terrible, bitter, bitter pill there, and we had to go back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When we came back to our town, the whole town was burned down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One Pollock-- when the-- when the German army came into our little town, one Pollock went on the roof and start shooting.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then the whole German took four corners of the little town and burned it down.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then we had no place to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then we all went-- we had a big synagogue.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then we slept over at the synagogue two or three nights, the whole town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And after that, everybody, my father-- should he rest in peace-- rented a room, another place with another family together, not by ourselves, like partners.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He would enter this apartment with another couple.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We lived there maybe not too long, because they pushed us to-- they made a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "After 1939, a very short time, maybe-- I don't remember how long this took, and they give us, like, four or five blocks-- streets-- and all the Jews had to live in one place.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They give us a room, I remember like now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we all lived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And my-- my older sister got just married before the war, and she was pregnant.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I don't remember when she had the baby.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think it was right after-- in middle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I mean, like 1940, and we were already in the-- the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto was like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
